<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='748520' id='t-748520'>It is this participation
in peacekeeping missions</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='752080' id='t-752080'>that has led to the resolution
of many civil wars.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='756760' id='t-756760'>My soldiers use the gun
as an instrument of peace.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:54
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='763280' id='t-763280'>And this is exactly
why failed states are so dangerous.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='768640' id='t-768640'>Failed states have no legitimized,
democratically controlled use of force.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='774240' id='t-774240'>Failed states do not know of the gun
as an instrument of peace and stability.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='781600' id='t-781600'>That is why failed states can drag down
