<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='874280' id='t-874280'>meet somewhere in the middle.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='876920' id='t-876920'>Until that day comes,
I stand for my father</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='881960' id='t-881960'>who tried to shoot the Nazis
