<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='886200' id='t-886200'>I stand for my men and women
who are prepared to risk their lives</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='892280' id='t-892280'>for a less violent world for all of us.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='897000' id='t-897000'>I stand for this soldier
who suffered partial hearing loss</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='902920' id='t-902920'>and sustained permanent
