</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:23
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='912600' id='t-912600'>Ladies and gentlemen,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='914400' id='t-914400'>until the day comes
