<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='970680' id='t-970680'>and we cannot let them down.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
16:25
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='974640' id='t-974640'>I hope you will respect my soldiers,</span>
