<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='990080' id='t-990080'>just like all of us here today.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
16:44
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='993880' id='t-993880'>Thank you very much.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
16:46
